text: Mechetlino () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Mechetlinsky Selsoviet, Salavatsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 713 as of 2010. There are 6 streets. == Geography == It is located 24 km from Maloyaz. == References == Category:Rural localities in Salavatsky District
title: Mechetlino
